xpress.co.uk/EXCLUSIVE-New-Avengers-film-8216-shot-Dover/story-21248339-detail/story.html |work=Dover Express |accessdate=2014-06-18 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6QPAnEWCu?url=http://www.dover-express.co.uk/EXCLUSIVE-New-Avengers-film-8216-shot-Dover/story-21248339-detail/story.html |archivedate=2014-06-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，7月在[[伦敦警察厅|伦敦警察厅]]训练场拍摄，此处在片中作为索科维亚的一个城市<ref name="WhedonTwins" /><ref name="BuzzFeed">{{cite web |url=http://www.buzzfeed.com/adambvary/thor-captain-america-avengers-age-of-ultron-set-visit |title=What’s At Stake For Thor, Captain America, And The "Avengers" Franchise |last=Vary |first=Adam |publisher=[[BuzzFeed|BuzzFeed]] |date=2014-10-27 |accessdate=2014-10-27 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6TdunXWCr?url=http://www.buzzfeed.com/adambvary/thor-captain-america-avengers-age-of-ultron-set-visit |archivedate=2014-10-27 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。此外，剧组还在[[孟加拉国|孟加拉国]][[吉大港市|吉大港市]]吉大港拆船码头和[[纽约|纽约]]市取景<ref name="FilmingUS">{{cite web |url=http://screenrant.com/ant-man-movie-locations-edgar-wright/ |title='Ant-Man' Not Shooting in Edgar Wright's Homeland But Will Embrace His Style |last=Keyes |first=Rob |publisher=Screen Rant |date=2013-11-27 |accessdate=2013-11-27 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6LRYGZZfx?url=http://screenrant.com/ant-man-movie-locations-edgar-wright/ |archivedate=2013-11-27 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="GotGAvengersFeature">{{cite av media|people=[[Joss_Whedon|Joss Whedon]], [[Kevin_Feige|Kevin Feige]], Jeremy Latcham|year=2014|title=Exclusive look at Marvel's Avengers: Age of Ultron|location=Guardians of the Galaxy Blu-ray|publisher=Walt Disney Home Entertainment}}</ref>。8月6日，韦登在社交媒体上宣布已经完成本片的主体拍摄工作<ref name="WhedonTweet" />。

在[[谢珀顿|谢珀顿]]及英国其他地区的拍摄让韦登得到“许多不同的景观、纹理和氛围”，并给予电影与前作不同的调色板和新鲜的美感<ref name="EmpireApril2014">{{cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=40833 |title=Joss Whedon Talks Avengers: Age Of Ultron |last=de Semlyen |first=Phil |work=Empire |date=2014-04-24 |accessdate=2014-04-24 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6P51kR1o6?url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=40833 |archivedate=2014-04-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。韦登还表示：“我们所拍的这部电影（与第一部电影）很不同。我用了许多摄像头，用长镜头拍摄，这是我一般不会做的”，他打算把电影拍成一部纪录片<ref name="WhedonTHRMar2015">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/joss-whedon-avengers-sequel-nightmare-779120 |title=Joss Whedon: 'Avengers' Sequel Was a "Nightmare" Due to Expanded Superhero Cast |last=Ritman |first=Alex |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2015-03-04 |accessdate=2015-03-04 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Wn8s6EVa?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/joss-whedon-avengers-sequel-nightmare-779120 |archivedate=2015-03-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。布景师查尔斯·伍德建立了一套巨大的新复仇者大厦，是漫威电影有史以来最大型的建筑之一。该场景与环境和楼层有多重联系<ref name="13Facts" />。为了描绘快银的速度特效，这些场景用超高速摄影机拍摄，后与由泰勒-约翰逊使用常规速度拍摄的场景相结合<ref name="WhedonTwins" />。

=== 后期制作 ===
[[File:New_Avengers_Training_Facility.jpg|thumb]]
2014年2月，[[光影魔幻工业|光影魔幻工业]]宣布计划开放位于伦敦的设施，表示《复仇者联盟2：奥创纪元》会是本次拓展的催化剂<ref name="ILM">{{cite news |last=Cohen |first=David |date=2014-02-11 |title='Star Wars,' 'Avengers' Spawn Industrial Light & Magic's London Expansion |url=http://variety.com/2014/biz/news/industrial-light-magic-london-star-wars-avengers-1201099729/ |work=Variety |accessdate=2014-02-11 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6NKySmgkP?url=http://variety.com/2014/biz/news/industrial-light-magic-london-star-wars-avengers-1201099729/ |archivedate=2014-02-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。光影魔幻工业开发了名为“Muse”的新运动捕捉系统，能更好地结合不同的需要捕捉演员的表演<ref name="ILM2">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/10/16/ilm-london-launch-updates-on-star-wars-episode-vii-avengers-age-of-ultron |title=ILM London Launch: Updates on Star Wars Episode VII & Avengers: Age of Ultron |last=Ashurst |first=Sam |publisher=IGN |date=2014-10-16 |accessdate=2014-10-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6TNJhbus5?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/10/16/ilm-london-launch-updates-on-star-wars-episode-vii-avengers-age-of-ultron |archivedate=2014-10-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。鲁法洛在谈到动作捕捉过程时表示：“我们已经做了很多动作捕捉。由于现在面部捕捉和动作捕捉可以共同完成，你能得到更多身为演员的余地......而不像以往[[CGI|CGI]]的基本占位符，该项技术变得更具协作性。演员真的能给它增加表演。现在这项技术又向前迈进了一步......更重要的是把它放到第一单元的制作中，但他们现在同样开始关心动作捕捉......我认为动作捕捉能让我们以令人难以置信的新方式投入到表演中，我们以前可没有过这种木偶般的体验。你知道，你不再被年龄、体重、身高等你身为人的特性所缩小。这些都不不再重要了。所以走进神秘感是让人感到兴奋的地方<ref name="IGNHulkOct2014">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/10/28/avengers-age-of-ultron-mark-ruffalo-says-theres-a-confrontation-coming-between-the-hulk-and-banner?page=2 |title=Avengers: Age of Ultron Mark Ruffalo Says There's A Confrontation Coming Between The Hulk And Banner |last=Cornet |first=Roth |publisher=IGN |date=2014-10-28 |accessdate=2014-11-03 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ToWAnhLP?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/10/28/avengers-age-of-ultron-mark-ruffalo-says-theres-a-confrontation-coming-between-the-hulk-and-banner?page=2 |archivedate=2014-11-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

2014年6月，IMAX公司宣布影片IMAX版本的发行将转换为IMAX 3D<ref name=IMAX3D>{{cite web|title=The Avengers: Age of Ultron An IMAX 3D Experience|url=https://www.imax.com/movies/m/the-avengers-age-of-ultron-an-imax-3d-experience/|publisher=[[IMAX|IMAX]]|accessdate=2014-06-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023115139/https://www.imax.com/movies/m/the-avengers-age-of-ultron-an-imax-3d-experience/|archivedate=2014-10-23}}</ref>。2014年8月，[[斯特兰·斯卡斯加德|斯特兰·斯卡斯加德]]透露将出演埃里克·沙维奇一角<ref name="Skarsgard">{{cite web |url=http://www.independent.ie/entertainment/movies/skarsgard-fine-with-avengers-nudity-30512798.html |title=Skarsgard fine with Avengers nudity |work=[[Irish_Independent|Irish Independent]] |date=2014-08-16 |accessdate=2014-08-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RsSgzXRK?url=http://www.independent.ie/entertainment/movies/skarsgard-fine-with-avengers-nudity-30512798.html |archivedate=2014-08-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2014年10月，执行制片人维多利亚·阿隆索表示，电影预计出现7到12家视觉特效公司制作的3000个特效镜头<ref name="IGNHulkOct2014"/>。2014年11月，[[伊德瑞斯·艾尔巴|伊德瑞斯·艾尔巴]]证实他将出演[[海姆達爾_(漫威漫畫)|海姆達爾]]一角，而[[汤姆·希德勒斯顿|汤姆·希德勒斯顿]]将出演洛基<ref name="Elba">{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/11195704/Idris-Elba-interview-Marvel-movies-are-torture.html |title=Idris Elba interview: Marvel movies are 'torture' |last=McLean |first=Craig |publisher=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |location=UK |date=2014-11-02 |accessdate=2014-11-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Tmmt9DA3?url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/11195704/Idris-Elba-interview-Marvel-movies-are-torture.html |archivedate=2014-11-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，否认了费格此前洛基将不会参演本剧的断言<ref name="Loki">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/10/28/marvel-studios-boss-kevin-feige-on-the-possibility-of-thor-3 |title=Marvel Studios Boss Kevin Feige on the Possibility of Thor 3 |last=Vejvoda |first=Jim |publisher=IGN]date=2013-10-28 |accessdate=2013-10-28 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6TmrwDVu5?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/10/28/marvel-studios-boss-kevin-feige-on-the-possibility-of-thor-3 |archivedate=2014-11-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>
。温登后来解释艾尔巴和阿特维尔将在复仇者们探索绯红女巫的超能力一幕中出现<ref name="WhedonTweet">{{cite web |date=2014-08-06 |first=Joss |last=Whedon |authorlink=Joss Whedon |title=Avengers 2 Wrapped What the hell do I do now? |publisher=Twitter |url=https://twitter.com/josswhedon/status/497108578109784064 |accessdate=2014-08-06 |archivedate=2014-08-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RdHfVz7g?url=https://twitter.com/josswhedon/status/497108578109784064 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2014年12月，韩国女演员金秀贤宣布饰演赵海伦博士<ref name="ClaudiaKim">{{cite web |url=http://collider.com/avengers-age-of-ultron-image-group/ |title=The Gang’s All Here in New 'Avengers: Age of Ultron' Image |last=Chitwood |first=Adam |publisher=Collider.com |date=2014-12-29 |accessdate=2014-12-29 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6VCGd604G?url=http://collider.com/avengers-age-of-ultron-image-group/ |archivedate=2014-12-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="HelenCho">{{cite web |url=http://screenrant.com/avengers-2-fun-facts/ |title=‘Avengers 2′ Facts & Videos: Details on New Characters, Costumes, Tech & Weapons |last=Keyes |first=Rob |publisher=Screen Rant |date=2015-04-03 |accessdate=2015-04-03 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6XWLcSKuu?url=http://screenrant.com/avengers-2-fun-facts/ |archivedate=2015-04-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。其他的场景预定于2015年1月在[[松林制片厂|松林制片厂]]开机<ref name="Pickup">{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2852442/BAZ-BAMIGBOYE-return-star-Avengers-Blighty.html |title=The return of the star Avengers – to Blighty |last=Bamigboye |first=Baz |work=Daily Mail |location=UK |date=2014-11-27 |accessdate=2014-11-28 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6UQTf8adx?url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2852442/BAZ-BAMIGBOYE-return-star-Avengers-Blighty.html |archivedate=2014-11-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2015年2月，漫威在宣传材料中证实索尔金将在影片中饰演尤利西斯·克劳<ref name="SerkisKlaw">{{cite web |url=http://www.stitchkingdom.com/disney-the-avengers-age-ultron-stills-behindthescenes-high-resolution-watermark-free-74269/ |title=‘The Avengers: Age of Ultron’ New Stills, Behind-the-Scenes in High Resolution; Serkis Confirmed as Klaw |publisher=Stitch Kingdom |date=2015-02-03 |accessdate=2015-02-04 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6W4oncLXO?url=http://www.stitchkingdom.com/disney-the-avengers-age-ultron-stills-behindthescenes-high-resolution-watermark-free-74269/ |archivedate=2015-02-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="CharacterDescriptions">{{cite web |url=http://movies.inquirer.net/16982/get-to-know-the-avengers-as-they-assemble-for-new-adventure |title=Get to Know the ‘Avengers’ as They Assemble for New Adventure |publisher=Inquirer.com |date=2015-04-03 |accessdate=2015-04-04 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6XXDWdCW7?url=http://movies.inquirer.net/16982/get-to-know-the-avengers-as-they-assemble-for-new-adventure |archivedate=2015-04-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。月底，[[安东尼·麦凯|安东尼·麦凯]]透过影片官方海报演职员名单部分证实将再度饰演猎鹰山姆·威尔逊<ref name="Mackie">{{cite web |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/the-gangs-all-here-in-the-official-avengers-age-of-ultron-poster/ |title=The Gang’s All Here in the Official ‘Avengers: Age of Ultron’ Poster [UPDATED] |last=Lussier |first=Germain |publisher=/Film |date=2015-02-24 |accessdate=2015-02-24 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Wamlu3ih?url=http://www.slashfilm.com/the-gangs-all-here-in-the-official-avengers-age-of-ultron-poster/ |archivedate=2015-02-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2015年4月初，[[琳达·卡德里尼|琳达·卡德里尼]]和[[朱莉·德尔比|朱莉·德尔比]]宣布参演<ref name="Delpy">{{cite web |url=http://screenrant.com/avengers-2-cast-julie-deply-linda-cardellini/ |title=‘Avengers 2′ Premiere Sheet Reveals Additional Cast Member [Updated] |last=Outlaw |first=Kofi |publisher=Screen Rant |date=2015-04-02 |accessdate=2015-04-03 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6XW7I0awS?url=http://screenrant.com/avengers-2-cast-julie-deply-linda-cardellini/ |archivedate=2015-04-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="Cardellini" />。同时，惠登表示电影不会按照漫威电影宇宙电影惯例提供[[片尾彩蛋|片尾彩蛋]]。温登试图想出片尾彩蛋，但认为不能把“沙威玛式场景”放在电影首位。他解释道：“似乎电影不能故技重施了，我们希望这种感觉是对的。制作续集的第一条要则是充分利用时间来做其他的事情。不再用《[[夺宝奇兵|夺宝奇兵]]》式的枪战把戏是不同的。尽管往其他方面去想，不去尝试触及同一个高潮，因为人们会厌倦的。”然而费格澄清“电影在演职员名单前会有片段，但不会在演职员名单后带彩蛋<ref name="Cardellini">{{cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/04/07/avengers-age-ultron-wont-have-post-credit-scene-joss-whedon-says |title=Avengers: Age of Ultron won't have a post-credit scene, Joss Whedon says |last=Breznican |first=Anthony |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2015-04-07 |accessdate=2015-04-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6XcOItbWo?url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/04/07/avengers-age-ultron-wont-have-post-credit-scene-joss-whedon-says |archivedate=2015-04-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。”

